732841f-b.title: Recreation and hobbies - Children playing.
732841f-b.text:
Recreations and Hobbies: Children playing in the snow
the curb on East 6lst Street between First and Second
Avenues. The photographer's vantage point is given as
No, 111 East 6lst Street.
Gift of B. Hoffman  Early 1914
MAY BE REPRODUCED  No's 1-2
